NK013(pa)012:0: dpal gsang ba snying po'i brgyud pa rin po cher gsol smon ku mud phreng ba bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)012:1: e wam rang bzhin rdo rje dril bu 'chang //
NK013(pa)012:2: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin rol pa'i gar gyis sgegs //
NK013(pa)012:3: bde stong rang bzhin kha sbyor bdun gyis bdag /
NK013(pa)012:4: lhan skyes rang bzhin rdo rje sems dpa' rgyal //
NK013(pa)012:5: gsang ba'i bdag po rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga //
NK013(pa)012:6: lung bstan rdo rje ku ku r+aa dza'i zhabs //
NK013(pa)012:7: sh+aakya su tri sa brgyad sems ma la //
NK013(pa)012:8: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:9: rdo rje yon tan gzungs dang h+aum ka ra //
NK013(pa)012:10: pra b+ha ha sti sangs rgyas gsang ba'i zhabs //
NK013(pa)012:11: slob dpon pad+ma pan chen bi ma lar //
NK013(pa)012:12: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:13: rin chen mchog dang gye re mchog skyong ba //
NK013(pa)012:14: rgyal ba yon tan gnubs chen rin po che //
NK013(pa)012:15: yon tan rgya mtsho ye shes rgya mtsho la //
NK013(pa)012:16: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:17: blo gros byang chub bde gshegs zur po che //
NK013(pa)012:18: shes rab grags pa gsang bdag sgro phug pa //
NK013(pa)012:19: rdzogs chen par grags bla ma rin po che //
NK013(pa)012:20: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:21: sku gsum mngon du gyur pa'i kahthoga pa //
NK013(pa)012:22: de sras sa bcu'i dbang phyug gtsang ston zhabs //
NK013(pa)012:23: thugs rje mtshungs med byams pa 'bum pa la //
NK013(pa)012:24: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:25: nam mkha' rdo rje thugs rje ye shes dang //
NK013(pa)012:26: ston pa dbang 'byor rje btsun dpal 'bar ba //
NK013(pa)012:27: mgon po rgyal mtshan tshul khrims rgyal mtshan la //
NK013(pa)012:28: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:29: d+harma kla k+sha ye shes rgyal mtshan rje //
NK013(pa)012:30: nam mkha' rgyal mtshan mtshungs med nam mkha' dpal /
NK013(pa)012:31: nam mkha' rgya mtsho chos kyi dbang po la //
NK013(pa)012:32: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:33: bsod nams rdo rje he pa chos 'byung dang //
NK013(pa)012:34: sh+aakya bkra shis rin chen rdo rje'i zhabs //
NK013(pa)012:35: sangs rgyas bkra shis sh+aakya tshe ring la //
NK013(pa)012:36: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:37: u rgyan phun tshogs thugs kyi rdo rje ba //
NK013(pa)012:38: blo gros chen po rje btsun bla ma'i zhabs //
NK013(pa)012:39: dpal ldan rdor sems dkyil 'khor dbang phyug dngos //
NK013(pa)012:40: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol /
NK013(pa)012:42: / 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du //
NK013(pa)012:43: dam po'i mdzod 'chang kun bzang dgongs pa'i rtsal //
NK013(pa)012:44: mngon rdzogs dus gsum sgyu 'phrul bla ma la //
NK013(pa)012:45: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:46: lhun sdug zhi tshul sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang //
NK013(pa)012:47: rab 'bar dpal chen khrag 'thung 'khor lo'i lha //
NK013(pa)012:48: gnas yul d+aak+ki ma mgon bstan srung la //
NK013(pa)012:49: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)012:50: bka' rgyud rnams la gsol ba btab pa yis //
NK013(pa)012:51: bdag cag slob 'bangs 'khor bcas ma lus kun //
NK013(pa)012:52: phyi yis g.yeng bas bar du mi chod cing //
NK013(pa)012:53: lta spyod ting 'dzin sgom pa ro mnyam shog /
NK013(pa)012:54: 'di las phyi ma rang las gzhan gyi don //
NK013(pa)012:55: gtso cher shes nas rmad byung byang chub kyi //
NK013(pa)012:56: spyod pa slob cing dpal ldan bla ma las //
NK013(pa)012:57: rnam dag dbang bzhis bdag rgyud smin par shog /
NK013(pa)012:58: rtogs bya gzhi rgyud dpal ldan gsang ba snying /
NK013(pa)012:60: / 'ching gral med pa'i gnas lugs gdod ma'i gshis //
NK013(pa)012:61: bden pa dbyer med rtogs byed thabs mchog lam //
NK013(pa)012:62: lung gi spyi rgyud chen po gtan 'bebs shog /
NK013(pa)012:63: shes rab gsum gyis sems la legs bskyed de //
NK013(pa)012:64: thabs kyis nges dang shes rab rnam grol lam //
NK013(pa)012:65: shes 'jug rim dang cig char dbang po bzhin //
NK013(pa)012:66: rtogs goms lam gyur rig 'dzin bzhi 'grub shog /
NK013(pa)012:67: lam gyi cha rkyen lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang //
NK013(pa)012:68: dam tshig phrin sgrub ting 'dzin mchod sngags rgya //
NK013(pa)012:69: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu la legs mkhas shing //
NK013(pa)012:70: bskyed rdzogs rim gnyis mtha' ru phyin par shog /
NK013(pa)012:71: grub pa mthar phyin 'bras chos nyer lnga'i bdag /
NK013(pa)012:72: dang po'i sangs rgyas thugs kyi thig le las //
NK013(pa)012:73: bgrang yas 'gro la mkha' khyab sprul pa'i nyi //
NK013(pa)012:74: phun tshogs phan bde'i 'od stong rgyas par shog /
NK013(pa)012:75: ces pa'ang chos kyi rgya mtshos 'jug pa bde ba'i phyir bkod pa'o //
